Ordered By Priority
-------------------

const - prevent writing to const vars

cpp - remove static vars from pp.c - multi-file processing. or limit to one file?

cc -E dir/x.c
doesn't work, but
cd dir; cc -E x.c
does

-W code in cc.c
-g in cc.c and eventually cc1.c with stabs/dwarf

options:
	warn on "{ 1, 2, 3, }" - final comma
	warn on ?:

fix "1 - 2 + 3"

errno - particularly BSD-systems

cc -MM *.c

typedefs

struct parsing

32-bit code gen

cc accepts multiple input source files

general lhs assignment:
	(b ? x : y) = 5;
	^-- note: gnu extension
	(x ? a : b)(2); // similarly
	(x = y) = 2; // assign to x

assembly optimisation - remove asm_temp()

({ expr; })
parsing

for(...){
}else{
	printf("for not entered");
}

signed vs unsigned:
jl, jle, jg, jge
vs
jb, jbe, ja, jae - above + below
